#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bac_calculator.html:5
msgid ""
"Calculate blood alcohol content (BAC) based on drinks consumed, weight, "
"gender, and time. Estimate when you'll be safe to drive."
