#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:366
msgid "What is Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR)?"
msgstr "O que é Taxa Metabólica Basal (TMB)?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR) is the number of calories your body needs to "
"perform basic life-sustaining functions while at complete rest. These "
"functions include breathing, circulation, cell production, brain and nerve "
"function, and maintaining body temperature."
msgstr ""
"A Taxa Metabólica Basal (TMB) é o número de calorias que seu corpo precisa "
"para realizar funções básicas de manutenção da vida enquanto está em repouso"
" completo. Essas funções incluem respiração, circulação, produção celular, "
"função cerebral e nervosa e manutenção da temperatura corporal."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:371
#, python-format
msgid ""
"BMR accounts for approximately 60-75%% of your total daily calorie "
"expenditure. It's the minimum number of calories you need to consume daily "
"to maintain basic bodily functions."
msgstr ""
"A TMB é responsável por aproximadamente 60-75% do seu gasto calórico diário "
"total. É o número mínimo de calorias que você precisa consumir diariamente "
"para manter as funções corporais básicas."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:377
msgid "What is Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE)?"
msgstr "O que é Gasto Energético Diário Total (TDEE)?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:379
msgid ""
"Total Daily Energy Expenditure (TDEE) is your total daily calorie burn, "
"including BMR plus calories burned through physical activity, exercise, and "
"the thermic effect of food (calories burned digesting food)."
msgstr ""
"O gasto total diário de energia (TDEE) é a queima total diária de calorias, "
"incluindo a TMB mais as calorias queimadas por meio de atividade física, "
"exercícios e o efeito térmico dos alimentos (calorias queimadas na digestão "
"dos alimentos)."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:382
msgid ""
"TDEE = BMR × Activity Multiplier. This represents the total number of "
"calories you burn in a day, which is crucial for weight management."
msgstr ""
"TDEE = TMB × Multiplicador de atividade. Isso representa o número total de "
"calorias que você queima por dia, o que é crucial para o controle de peso."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:388
msgid "BMR Calculation Formulas"
msgstr "Fórmulas de cálculo de TMB"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:391
msgid "Mifflin-St Jeor Equation (Recommended)"
msgstr "Equação de Mifflin-St Jeor (recomendado)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:393
msgid "Most accurate for modern populations. Considered the gold standard."
msgstr "Mais preciso para populações modernas. Considerado o padrão ouro."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:396
msgid "Men: BMR = 10 × weight(kg) + 6.25 × height(cm) - 5 × age(years) + 5"
msgstr ""
"Homens: TMB = 10 × peso (kg) + 6,25 × altura (cm) - 5 × idade (anos) + 5"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:397
msgid ""
"Women: BMR = 10 × weight(kg) + 6.25 × height(cm) - 5 × age(years) - 161"
msgstr ""
"Mulheres: TMB = 10 × peso (kg) + 6,25 × altura (cm) - 5 × idade (anos) - 161"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:401
msgid "Harris-Benedict Equation (Revised)"
msgstr "Equação de Harris-Benedict (revisada)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:403
msgid ""
"Older formula, still widely used. May overestimate BMR for some individuals."
msgstr ""
"Fórmula mais antiga, ainda amplamente utilizada. Pode superestimar a TMB "
"para alguns indivíduos."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:406
msgid ""
"Men: BMR = 13.397 × weight(kg) + 4.799 × height(cm) - 5.677 × age(years) + "
"88.362"
msgstr ""
"Homens: TMB = 13,397 × peso (kg) + 4,799 × altura (cm) - 5,677 × idade "
"(anos) + 88,362"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:407
msgid ""
"Women: BMR = 9.247 × weight(kg) + 3.098 × height(cm) - 4.330 × age(years) + "
"447.593"
msgstr ""
"Mulheres: TMB = 9,247 × peso (kg) + 3,098 × altura (cm) - 4,330 × idade "
"(anos) + 447,593"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:411
msgid "Katch-McArdle Formula"
msgstr "Fórmula Katch-McArdle"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"Most accurate when body fat percentage is known. Uses lean body mass instead"
" of total weight."
msgstr ""
"Mais preciso quando o percentual de gordura corporal é conhecido. Usa massa "
"corporal magra em vez do peso total."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:416
msgid "BMR = 370 + (21.6 × Lean Body Mass in kg)"
msgstr "TMB = 370 + (21,6 × massa corporal magra em kg)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:419
msgid ""
"Note: This calculator estimates lean body mass based on gender averages."
msgstr ""
"Nota: Esta calculadora estima a massa corporal magra com base nas médias de "
"gênero."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:427
msgid "Activity Level Multipliers"
msgstr "Multiplicadores de nível de atividade"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:429
