msgstr "Selecione seu gênero (afeta a fórmula usada)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:439
msgid "Enter your age, height, and weight"
msgstr "Insira sua idade, altura e peso"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:444
msgid "Review charts and body composition analysis"
msgstr "Revise gráficos e análise de composição corporal"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:455
msgid ""
"Measure just below the larynx (Adam's apple) with the tape sloping slightly "
"downward at the front. Keep the tape horizontal and snug but not tight."
msgstr ""
"Meça logo abaixo da laringe (pomo de Adão) com a fita ligeiramente inclinada"
" para baixo na frente. Mantenha a fita horizontal e confortável, mas não "
"apertada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:461
msgid ""
"Measure at your navel level (belly button), not at the narrowest point. "
"Stand straight, breathe normally, and measure at the end of a normal breath."
" Keep the tape level and parallel to the floor."
msgstr ""
"Meça na altura do umbigo (umbigo), não no ponto mais estreito. Fique em pé, "
"respire normalmente e meça no final de uma respiração normal. Mantenha a "
"fita nivelada e paralela ao chão."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:467
msgid ""
"Measure around the hips at the widest point. This is typically around the "
"buttocks area. Keep the tape measure horizontal and parallel to the floor."
msgstr ""
"Meça ao redor dos quadris no ponto mais largo. Isso geralmente ocorre na "
"área das nádegas. Mantenha a fita métrica horizontal e paralela ao chão."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:473
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:388
msgid "Tip:"
msgstr "Dica:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:473
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:388
msgid ""
"For best accuracy, take measurements in the morning before eating, and "
"measure multiple times to ensure consistency."
msgstr ""
"Para melhor precisão, faça medições pela manhã, antes de comer, e meça "
"várias vezes para garantir a consistência."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:485
msgid ""
"Your estimated body fat percentage based on the US Navy formula. This is an "
"estimate and may vary from other measurement methods like DEXA scan or "
"hydrostatic weighing."
msgstr ""
"Seu percentual estimado de gordura corporal com base na fórmula da Marinha "
"dos EUA. Esta é uma estimativa e pode variar de outros métodos de medição, "
"como varredura DEXA ou pesagem hidrostática."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:491
msgid ""
"The total weight of fat in your body, calculated as a percentage of your "
"total body weight."
msgstr ""
"O peso total de gordura no seu corpo, calculado como uma percentagem do seu "
"peso corporal total."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:497
msgid ""
"The total weight of everything except fat: muscle, bone, organs, and water. "
"Higher lean mass generally indicates better fitness and health."
msgstr ""
"O peso total de tudo, exceto gordura: músculos, ossos, órgãos e água. Maior "
"massa magra geralmente indica melhor condicionamento físico e saúde."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:503
#, python-format
msgid ""
"An estimated weight at which you would have an ideal body fat percentage "
"(10-20%% for men, 18-28%% for women) while maintaining your current lean "
"mass."
msgstr ""
"Um peso estimado no qual você teria um percentual de gordura corporal ideal "
"(10-20%% para homens, 18-28%% para mulheres), mantendo sua massa magra "
"atual."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:509
msgid ""
"Your body fat classification based on gender-specific ranges. This helps you"
" understand where you stand relative to health and fitness standards."
msgstr ""
"Sua classificação de gordura corporal com base em faixas específicas de "
"gênero. Isso ajuda você a entender sua posição em relação aos padrões de "
"saúde e condicionamento físico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:523
msgid ""
"This calculator provides ESTIMATES based on body measurements. Actual body "
"fat percentage may vary when measured with more precise methods like DEXA "
"scan, hydrostatic weighing, or BodPod."
msgstr ""
"Esta calculadora fornece ESTIMATIVAS baseadas em medidas corporais. O "
"percentual real de gordura corporal pode variar quando medido com métodos "
"mais precisos, como varredura DEXA, pesagem hidrostática ou BodPod."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:529
msgid ""
"Accurate measurements are crucial. Measure at the same time of day, "
"preferably in the morning before eating, and ensure the tape measure is "
"level and snug but not tight."
msgstr ""
"Medições precisas são cruciais. Meça na mesma hora do dia, de preferência de"
" manhã antes de comer, e certifique-se de que a fita métrica esteja nivelada"
" e confortável, mas não apertada."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:535
msgid ""
"Body fat percentage is just one indicator of health. Consider other factors "
"like blood pressure, cholesterol, blood sugar, and overall fitness level."
msgstr ""
"O percentual de gordura corporal é apenas um indicador de saúde. Considere "
"outros fatores como pressão arterial, colesterol, açúcar no sangue e nível "
"geral de condicionamento físico."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_fat_calculator.html:541
msgid ""
"This calculator is for educational and informational purposes only. Always "
"consult with a healthcare provider or registered dietitian for personalized "
"health advice."
msgstr ""
